step 1 : Create Instance 
step 2: Go  to the create vollume and select vollume 
step 3: Then select action and attached the vollume
step 4: Go to the instance and check the storage 
step 5 : Connect to the ec2 user on ssh in cli 
step 6: lsblk check the partition 
step 7: fdisk /dev/xvdf
step 8: create partition
and enter defualt first sector and last sector and enter the parttion
step 9:lsblk ( check parttion is create )
step 10: mkfs /dev/xvdf1  (make the  filesystem)
step 11: create directory for the  mount
step 12 :mkdir /mnt/charan
step 13: ls /mnt/
step 14: mount /dev/xvdf1 /mnt/charan
you will see new volume mounted successfully.
